<taxonomicName id="4C589CA5FFCCFF9AFE9CBAB9E094F861" authorityName="Gilbert" authorityYear="1905" box="[319,434,1925,1951]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Paralepididae" genus="Lestidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aulopiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="130" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="nudum">
<emphasis id="B92C3B34FFCCFF9AFE9CBAB9E094F861" box="[319,434,1925,1951]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="130">Lt. nudum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Hawaii, 
<taxonomicName id="4C589CA5FFCCFF9AFDF9BAB9E3C1F861" authority="Ho &amp; Tsai &amp; Li, 2019" authorityName="Ho &amp; Tsai &amp; Li" authorityYear="2019" box="[602,743,1925,1951]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Paralepididae" genus="Lestidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aulopiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="130" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="orientale" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B92C3B34FFCCFF9AFDF9BAB9E3C1F861" box="[602,743,1925,1951]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="130">Lt. orientale</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B92C3B34FFCCFF9AFD4CBABAE26DF861" bold="true" box="[751,843,1925,1951]" pageId="16" pageNumber="130">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A21F864FFFCCFF9AFD4CBABAE26DF861" box="[751,843,1925,1951]" pageId="16" pageNumber="130" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
from 
<collectingCountry id="F34FA7B6FFCCFF9AFC31BABAE2C2F861" box="[914,996,1925,1951]" name="Taiwan" pageId="16" pageNumber="130">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F34FA7B6FFCCFF9AFBBDBABAE547F861" box="[1054,1121,1925,1951]" name="Japan" pageId="16" pageNumber="130">Japan</collectingCountry>
; and 
<taxonomicName id="4C589CA5FFCCFF9AFB3CBAB9E414F861" authorityName="Harry" authorityYear="1953" box="[1183,1330,1925,1951]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Paralepididae" genus="Lestidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aulopiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="130" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="prolixium">
<emphasis id="B92C3B34FFCCFF9AFB3CBAB9E414F861" box="[1183,1330,1925,1951]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="130">Lt. prolixium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the western Pacific Ocean. Two other species from the western Pacific Ocean is being studied in a separated work (Ho, unpub. data). The generic status of 
<taxonomicName id="4C589CA5FFCCFF9AFD81BAF1E381F819" authorityName="Graae" authorityYear="1967" box="[546,679,1997,2023]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Paralepididae" genus="Lestidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aulopiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="130" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bigelowi">
<emphasis id="B92C3B34FFCCFF9AFD81BAF1E381F819" box="[546,679,1997,2023]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="130">Lt. bigelowi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is still doubtful.
</paragraph>
